    <head><lb ed="X" n="0458b02"/>　　　　<persName key="A021348">一關逵</persName>傳</head>
    <p><anchor n="X.77.1524.0458b03"/><lb ed="X" n="0458b03"/><persName key="A021348">正逵</persName>。字<persName key="A021348">一關</persName>。<placeName key="PL000000020168">番陽</placeName>方氏子。初參<persName key="A008284">晦機</persName>。語已逸格絕塵。
        <lb ed="X" n="0458b04"/>機首肯。處以明窓。自是禪講諸老。競以書聘。欲令出
        <lb ed="X" n="0458b05"/>門下。逵不從。時<persName key="A001032">端元叟</persName>。說法<placeName key="PL000000011848">徑山</placeName>。人尊之為當代妙
        <lb ed="X" n="0458b06"/>喜。乃往從之。纔入門。<persName key="A001032">叟</persName>厲聲一喝。若聞雷霆。黏縛盡
        <lb ed="X" n="0458b07"/>脫。遽作禮。<persName key="A001032">叟</persName>曰。汝果何所見耶。問答數轉。皆愜<persName key="A001032">叟</persName>意。
        <lb ed="X" n="0458b08"/>顧左右曰。是般若位中人也。遂錄為子歸侍司。遷掌
        <lb ed="X" n="0458b09"/>記。後出世金陵之<placeName key="PL000000009072">崇因</placeName>。帝師廉其賢。授以<persName key="A021348">佛日普炤</persName>
        <lb ed="X" n="0458b10"/>之號。</p><p>
            <lb ed="X" n="0458b11"/>　<placeName key="PL000000011848">徑山</placeName>新志云。逵見<persName key="A007271">宋濂</persName>傳。而宋文集實無有。且帝
            <lb ed="X" n="0458b12"/>　師贈號。同<persName key="A001082">琦楚石</persName>。<persName key="A001082">楚石</persName>亦<persName key="A001032">元叟</persName>之嗣。大都<persName key="A001032">元叟</persName>法
        <lb ed="X" n="0458b13"/>　嗣滿天下。必有逵無疑。但不知新志據何書也。姑
        <lb ed="X" n="0458b14"/>　錄之。以備考。</p>
</div>
